title: Noget om Emma
overview: 27-year-old Vitus is stuck in a rut and generally lost in life until he meets Emma. She's everything he isn't. She's optimistic, adventurous, and follows her impulses. The two of them start seeing each other, yet Vitus leaves out the small detail that his ex-girlfriend is pregnant and has decided to keep the baby against his will. As their relationship evolves it turns out that Emma is carrying a much bigger secret. Will their love survive, when their secrets see the light of the day?
